{
  "stem": "8569.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember during the war-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] during the bombing of Warsaw, we met for the first time our next-door neighbors.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We met them in bomb shelters downstairs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And one day, they invited me to their house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was very dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So being a very polite and well-behaved girl, I immediately put on the light, and I was screamed at.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You are not supposed to put the light on!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I went home crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't know what it was all about, just to tell you how far removed we were from-- I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Of course, it was all straightened out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they happened to be an Orthodox family, who did not put on light on Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Must have been Friday night or something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's really hard for me to tell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Remember that when the war broke out in 1939, I was 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know that we used to get the Polish newspaper, but where exactly on the political spectrum my father belonged, I really couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know that as a result of our upbringing at school, I felt myself fiercely Polish patriotic.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I remember that when the Germans came to Poland, Warsaw was bombed out, and we had no water.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I used to go with Isabela to a place where there was main water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to take buckets and kettles to bring water into the house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it so happened that I saw the first Germans, that they had a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] camp kitchen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And while Isabela stood in the queue, I went off on a little hill.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was standing there looking around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was all different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the young German soldier came to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
